reviews.review_text:
DEAR MR. FANTASY Decent performance, good enough for the time.....but just when you think it's time to write off this show, suddenly comes the most impassioned, blistering, unforgettable version of DEAR MR. FANTASY the band ever played....!!

Average show raised from 2 to 4 stars simply on the strength of this STUPENDOUS version of DMFantasy...!!
